sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant React as React (BookingForm)
    participant Auth as AuthContext
    participant Flask as Flask API
    participant JWT as JWT Middleware
    participant CC as ConflictChecker
    participant DB as Database

    User->>React: Fill form and click Submit
    React->>Auth: getToken()
    Auth-->>React: JWT token
    React->>Flask: POST /api/bookings + Bearer token
    Flask->>JWT: Verify token signature & expiry
    JWT-->>Flask: user_id, role extracted

    Flask->>CC: checkConflict(room_id, date, start, end)
    CC->>DB: SELECT bookings WHERE overlap condition
    alt Conflict found
        DB-->>CC: Returns existing booking
        CC-->>Flask: Conflict detected
        Flask-->>React: HTTP 409 - Room already booked
        React-->>User: Show conflict warning
    else No conflict
        DB-->>CC: Empty result
        CC-->>Flask: Slot is free
        Flask->>DB: INSERT booking (status=pending)
        DB-->>Flask: booking_id returned
        Flask-->>React: HTTP 201 - Booking created
        React-->>User: Success message, redirect to /my-bookings
    end